OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782407919
OL,3,CCritical incidents at two hospitals as
OL,4,Cextreme weather impacts services
OL,6,FA critical incident at a Portsmouth
OL,7,Fhospital is continuing into a second
OL,8,Fday.
OL,10,FThe incident was first declared
OL,11,Fyesterday after the extreme heat
OL,12,Fcaused some of the chiller units at
OL,13,FQueen Alexandra Hospital to fail.
OL,15,FWhilst the chiller units are now up
OL,16,Fand running, the exceptionally hot
OL,17,Fweather has meant that cooling back
OL,18,Fdown vital infrastructure on site is
OL,19,Ftaking much longer than normal.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
