OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782407919
OL,3,CCritical incidents at two hospitals as
OL,4,Cextreme weather impacts services
OL,6,FThe hospital says 'critical clinical
OL,7,Fand digital services' are gradually
OL,8,Freturning, but this is happening
OL,9,Fslowly, and show the critical incident
OL,10,Fhas been extended so that services can
OL,11,Fcome back online in a controlled way.
OL,13,FIt added that some planned care and
OL,14,Fappointments will continue to be stood
OL,15,Fdown until temperatures have been
OL,16,Fstabilised but that anyone impacted
OL,17,Fwill be contacted directly, so
OL,18,Feveryone else should attend as normal.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782407919
OL,3,CCritical incidents at two hospitals as
OL,4,Cextreme weather impacts services
OL,6,FMichelle Stanley, Acting Chief
OL,7,FExecutive, Portsmouth Hospitals
OL,8,FUniversity NHS Trust, said: "Our teams
OL,9,Fhave worked hard to fix the initial
OL,10,Fissue and our chillers are now back
OL,11,Fand working.
OL,13,F"However, the extreme heat means the
OL,14,Fprocess of cooling key infrastructure
OL,15,Fis taking longer than hoped.
OL,17,F"With temperatures still high we are
OL,18,Fworking to bring back services in a
OL,19,Fcontrolled manner to ensure the safety
OL,20,Fof our patients and staff.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782407919
OL,3,CCritical incidents at two hospitals as
OL,4,Cextreme weather impacts services
OL,6,F"We would like to thank all our
OL,7,Fpartners in the region who have
OL,8,Fstepped in to help during the
OL,9,Fincident, their support has been
OL,10,Fgreatly appreciated."
OL,12,FThe hospital has emphasised that
OL,13,Fessential services continue to remain
OL,14,Favailable for anyone who needs them
OL,15,Fand say that anyone needing urgent
OL,16,Fmedical help, should contact NHS 111
OL,17,For dial 999.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@UO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
