SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782407919
OL,3,CCritical incidents at two hospitals as
OL,4,Cextreme weather impacts services
OL,6,FPatients who do not need to attend the
OL,7,Femergency department are being asked
OL,8,Fto bring plenty of water and to bring
OL,9,Fa maximum of one person with them.
OL,11,FThe hospital is also requesting that
OL,12,Fpeople use alternative healthcare
OL,13,Foptions for non-urgent medical issues
OL,14,Fwhenever possible, such as community
OL,15,Fpharmacies, GP practices, urgent
OL,16,Ftreatment centres and NHS 111.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
