CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782407919
OL,3,CCritical incidents at two hospitals as
OL,4,Cextreme weather impacts services
OL,6,FThe hospital has emphasised that
OL,7,Fessential services continue to remain
OL,8,Favailable for anyone who needs them
OL,9,Fand say that anyone needing urgent
OL,10,Fmedical help, should contact NHS 111
OL,11,For dial 999.
OL,13,FPatients who do not need to attend the
OL,14,Femergency department are being asked
OL,15,Fto bring plenty of water and to bring
OL,16,Fa maximum of one person with them.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
