FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782407919
OL,3,CCritical incidents at two hospitals as
OL,4,Cextreme weather impacts services
OL,6,FThe hospital are also requesting that
OL,7,Fpeople use alternative healthcare
OL,8,Foptions for non-urgent medical issues
OL,9,Fwhenever possible, such as community
OL,10,Fpharmacies, GP practices, urgent
OL,11,Ftreatment centres and NHS 111.
OL,13,FIt has also highlighted the importance
OL,14,Fof patients who are ready to leave
OL,15,Fhospital being collected promptly to
OL,16,Ffree up space for those that need it,
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
